The Saek tones are: 1 = /34/ mid level, slight rise at the end 2 = /11/ low level 3 = /31/ falling to low, with glottal constriction 4 = /454/ high rising-falling 5 = /52/ high falling 6 = /32/ mid level, with slight fall and glottal constriction
